OL,5,Clater
OL,7,F'People thought we were criminals':
OL,8,FSub-postmaster Peter Holloway is
OL,9,Fjoined by ITV News Correspondent Chloe
OL,10,FKeedy as he returns to the town he
OL,11,Ffled after the Horizon Scandal
OL,13,FThere are few things for which Peter
OL,14,FHolloway now counts himself lucky.
OL,15,FLiving near the coast in
OL,16,FNorthumberland is one of them. Him and
OL,17,Fhis wife Sue moved here, he says, "to
OL,18,Fget as far away as possible from where
OL,19,Fwe used to live".
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/14
