OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FPeter and Sue's old life was on a
OL,8,Fdifferent coast, more than 300 miles
OL,9,Faway. He lived in the Dorset village
OL,10,Fof West Lulworth, and ran the Post
OL,11,FOffice in Wareham, nearby.
OL,13,FThat was 15 years ago, before Peter
OL,14,Fwas suspended from his job by the Post
OL,15,FOffice, which, he says, had accused
OL,16,Fhim of stealing tens of thousands of
OL,17,Fpounds.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
