OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FThe money had gone missing from
OL,8,FPeter's branch, and the Post Office
OL,9,Fthreatened to prosecute him if he
OL,10,Fdidn't pay it back.
OL,12,F"I paid the losses out of our own
OL,13,Ffunds," he said. "So eventually it got
OL,14,Fto a point where we were basically
OL,15,Fworking for no money because we were
OL,16,Fpaying so much money each month to the
OL,17,FPost Office.
OL,19,F"I had to draw cash out on the credit
OL,20,Fcard to pay the staff.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
