OL,5,Clater
OL,7,F"They said you must be stealing, and I
OL,8,Fsaid 'why would I do that?' If money
OL,9,Fis short, I would have to pay it back.
OL,10,FWhy would I steal?"
OL,12,FThe shortfalls were caused by the now
OL,13,Fbut neither Peter, nor his customers,
OL,14,Fknew that at the time. Over the years,
OL,15,FPeter estimates he lost more than
OL,16,F#100,000.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/14
