OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FHow did he feel about doing that?
OL,8,F"Nervous," he told me.
OL,10,FHe explained he and Sue had been back
OL,11,Fonly once before, not long after they
OL,12,Fleft. But he said they were made to
OL,13,Ffeel unwelcome and found it too
OL,14,Fupsetting. They had vowed never to go
OL,15,Fback.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/14
