OL,5,Clater
OL,7,F"I never thought I'd be standing here
OL,8,Fagain in my life," Peter said, peering
OL,9,Fin through the door of his old Post
OL,10,FOffice. "I was really not looking
OL,11,Fforward to it. It brings back terrible
OL,12,Fmemories, but I know it's not my fault.
OL,14,F"The government and (the Post Office)
OL,15,Fare still not giving us our
OL,16,Fcompensation, they're not paying us
OL,17,Fback our money, they won't pay our
OL,18,Flegal fees.
OL,26,@vD@UpmvD@epn
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/14
