OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FThose that knew Peter welcomed him
OL,8,Fwith open arms, telling me that "he
OL,9,Fshould never have had to leave".
OL,11,FSome of Peter's old neighbours invited
OL,12,Fus in for a cup of tea and a catch up.
OL,13,FBut even Dave, a close friend who
OL,14,Falways stood by him, admitted there
OL,15,Fwas a time when he struggled to make
OL,16,Fsense of it all.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/14
