OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FHe is still waiting for repayment for
OL,8,Fwhat he lost, and is calling on the
OL,9,Fprime minister and the government to
OL,10,Fspeed up the compensation scheme, as
OL,11,Fwell as pay the legal fees of the
OL,12,Fgroup of sub-postmasters who took the
OL,13,FPost Office to court.
OL,15,FIt's taken 15 years and a TV drama to
OL,16,Fmake Peter finally feel his story
OL,17,Fwould be understood.
OL,19,FWhat he didn't know, as we drove back
OL,20,Ftowards the town of Wareham, is how
OL,21,Fmany people were waiting to hear it.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G11/14
