OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FWe had tracked down some of the old
OL,8,Fcustomers and friends he hadn't seen
OL,9,Fsince he left, who were waiting inside
OL,10,Fa community cafe to surprise Peter
OL,11,Fwith a banner that read "welcome back."
OL,13,FThey called him a "pillar of the
OL,14,Fcommunity", as Peter, becoming
OL,15,Femotional, told them he had been
OL,16,F"through hell".
OL,18,FHe told me he had been dreading this
OL,19,Ftrip, but said that, to his surprise,
OL,20,Fit had been part of a "healing
OL,21,Fprocess."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G12/14
