OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FHe never did blame the people here.
OL,8,FIt's the Post Office he says he can't
OL,9,Fforgive - for taking him away from
OL,10,Fthem for so long.
OL,12,FThe Post Office declined to comment on
OL,13,FPeter's story.
OL,15,FA Department for Business and Trade
OL,16,FSpokesperson said: "We are committed
OL,17,Fto righting the wrongs of the past,
OL,18,Fensuring sub-postmasters are rightly
OL,19,Fcompensated for the hardship they have
OL,20,Fendured."
